00:44:24,164 --> 00:44:25,704
Who?

542
00:44:25,704 --> 00:44:27,954
Who died?

543
00:44:28,974 --> 00:44:31,334
How could things go down like that?

544
00:44:32,444 --> 00:44:34,544
That shirt belongs to me.

545
00:44:34,544 --> 00:44:37,424
Hee Seop... Hee Seop knew everything already.

546
00:44:37,424 --> 00:44:40,554
He already knew what I did earlier that night!

547
00:44:50,304 --> 00:44:52,844
Hee Seop...

548
00:45:15,554 --> 00:45:18,154
That night...

549
00:45:20,154 --> 00:45:23,004
After he escaped,

550
00:45:23,924 --> 00:45:27,584
your brother came to see you.

551
00:45:27,584 --> 00:45:29,814
Right?

552
00:45:39,684 --> 00:45:43,154
That never happened!

553
00:45:44,174 --> 00:45:45,644
Hee Seop.

554
00:45:45,644 --> 00:45:47,754
Hee Seop.

555
00:45:47,754 --> 00:45:50,544
Hee Seop. Yes...

556
00:45:50,544 --> 00:45:53,274
Do you know what kind of place this is?

557
00:45:53,274 --> 00:45:56,364
The kind of place you can't even imagine.

558
00:45:56,364 --> 00:46:00,164
