559
00:46:00,164 --> 00:46:06,174
So if things go wrong here, no one will ever know what happened to you. Got it?

560
00:46:12,274 --> 00:46:14,464
But I-I...

561
00:46:14,464 --> 00:46:16,404
- I-I... 
 - Huh?

562
00:46:16,404 --> 00:46:17,534
Yeah?

563
00:46:17,534 --> 00:46:19,624
I'm ignorant, so...

564
00:46:21,134 --> 00:46:24,024
I don't know what that means.

565
00:46:25,414 --> 00:46:28,474
Oh, how tiresome. Tiresome.

566
00:46:28,474 --> 00:46:30,474
Tiresome!

567
00:46:40,044 --> 00:46:41,864
So now, do you remember?

568
00:46:41,864 --> 00:46:44,184
Are you going to tell us or what?

569
00:46:44,184 --> 00:46:46,304
I guess not yet! Let's go!

570
00:46:56,614 --> 00:46:58,324
 Brother?

571
00:47:00,474 --> 00:47:02,654
 What happened?

572
00:47:09,584 --> 00:47:11,004
 Hee Seop!

573
00:47:11,004 --> 00:47:12,714
 Brother!

574
00:47:23,574 --> 00:47:25,484
 Brother...

575
00:47:25,484 --> 00:47:26,974
 Hee Seop...

576
00:47:26,974 --> 00:47:28,574
 Yes?

577
00:47:29,600 --> 00:47:33,500
 Oh, what... w-what is this?

578
00:47:33,514 --> 00:47:35,804
 I'm asking you, what is this?

579
00:47:38,444 --> 00:47:41,034
 Brother, did you protest again?

580
00:47:43,024 --> 00:47:45,894
 D-Did you?

581
00:47:45,894 --> 00:47:48,294
 I'm sorry, Hee Seop.

582
00:47:49,794 --> 00:47:51,544
 I'm...

583
00:47:52,424 --> 00:47:54,624
 I'm sorry.

584
00:47:54,624 --> 00:47:57,674
 I told you not to do that kind of dangerous thing anymore!

585
00:47:57,674 --> 00:48:00,054
 I told you not to ever do that again!

586
00:48:18,420 --> 00:48:20,350
 Where did it go?

587
00:48:21,264 --> 00:48:23,444
 You bastard.

588
00:48:23,444 --> 00:48:26,084
 You idiot!

589
00:48:29,364 --> 00:48:31,284
 Did you forget everything?

590
00:48:31,284 --> 00:48:32,574
 Huh?

591
00:48:32,574 --> 00:48:34,774
 Did you forget about all this?

592
00:48:36,574 --> 00:48:38,174
 If I had forgotten,

593
00:48:39,134 --> 00:48:42,794
 would I be doing this, Hee Seop?

594
00:48:42,794 --> 00:48:45,064

Mom! Dad!

595
00:48:45,774 --> 00:48:47,124
 Something terrible is happening!

596
00:48:47,124 --> 00:48:50,864
 - There are gunshots in the streets, and people are dying! 
 - What?

597
00:48:50,864 --> 00:48:54,794
 Yoo Seop must've eaten something wrong, dear.

598
00:48:54,794 --> 00:48:58,254
 It's not even summer yet, and you must be having a heat stroke.

599
00:48:58,254 --> 00:48:59,634
 I'm serious!

600
00:48:59,634 --> 00:49:01,844
 Gosh, come in. Stop saying nonsense.

601
00:49:01,844 --> 00:49:03,464
 Jin Seop's mom!

602
00:49:03,464 --> 00:49:05,804
- Goodness! Jin Seop's mom! 
 - What?

603
00:49:05,804 --> 00:49:08,294
 I think you need to go to the city hospital!

604
00:49:08,294 --> 00:49:10,244
 - W-Why? 
 - What?

605
00:49:10,244 --> 00:49:12,074
 What are you talking about?

606
00:49:12,074 --> 00:49:16,564
 So many students in that school were shot while protesting,

607
00:49:16,564 --> 00:49:20,314
 and they're covered in straw bags left and right and pushed aside!

608
00:49:20,314 --> 00:49:24,204
 Jin Seop goes to that school, doesn't he?

609
00:49:24,204 --> 00:49:25,714
 Oh my god!

610
00:49:25,714 --> 00:49:27,554
 Mom!

611
00:49:27,554 --> 00:49:28,894
 Mom.

612
00:49:28,894 --> 00:49:33,424
 Your dad and I will be right back.

613
00:49:33,424 --> 00:49:36,654
 We'll go and find your brother.

614
00:49:36,654 --> 00:49:40,134
 Don't come outside no matter what, all right?

615
00:49:40,134 --> 00:49:42,124
 Mom...

616
00:49:42,124 --> 00:49:44,274
 If anything happens,

617
00:49:45,294 --> 00:49:48,504
 Yoo Seop and Hee Seop,

618
00:49:48,504 --> 00:49:53,314
 have pity on each other...

619
00:49:53,314 --> 00:49:57,734
 and the two of you should take good care of each other

620
00:49:57,734 --> 00:50:00,604
 and live a good life. Okay?

621
00:50:00,604 --> 00:50:02,274
 Mom...

622
00:50:02,274 --> 00:50:05,874
 You promised me, okay?

623
00:50:05,874 --> 00:50:07,804
 - Mom! 
 - Mom!

624
00:50:07,804 --> 00:50:10,544
 - Mom! 
 - Mom! Mom!

625
00:50:10,544 --> 00:50:12,874
 - Dad! 
 - Mom!

626
00:50:12,874 --> 00:50:15,144
 - Dad! 
 - Mom!

627
00:50:54,514 --> 00:50:57,004
 How could I forget that day?

628
00:50:57,894 --> 00:51:00,034
 Hee Seop.

629
00:51:01,254 --> 00:51:05,204
 How could I forget those gunshots?

630
00:51:05,204 --> 00:51:10,274
 Then, what about the promise we made with Mom?

631
00:51:10,274 --> 00:51:12,464
 How am I going to live if this happens to you?

632
00:51:12,464 --> 00:51:14,484
 Then, what do we do?

633
00:51:16,074 --> 00:51:17,384
 Huh?

634
00:51:18,594 --> 00:51:20,774
 Mom,

635
00:51:20,774 --> 00:51:22,864
 Dad,

636
00:51:22,864 --> 00:51:25,444
 our older brother,

637
00:51:25,444 --> 00:51:27,614
 we lost them all.

638
00:51:27,614 --> 00:51:29,974
 What do I do...

639
00:51:29,974 --> 00:51:32,524
 when I feel such injustice and resentment?

640
00:51:35,374 --> 00:51:39,174
 There's a fire inside me.

641
00:51:39,174 --> 00:51:43,804
 How can I live quietly when there's a fire inside me? How...

642
00:51:57,674 --> 00:51:59,904
 How can I live...

643
00:52:06,264 --> 00:52:09,604
 I just found someone I like, too.

644
00:52:10,724 --> 00:52:14,154
 I didn't even get to treat her nicely yet...

645
00:52:31,614 --> 00:52:33,594
 Hurry up and take off your shirt.

646
00:52:33,594 --> 00:52:35,234
 Okay?

647
00:52:35,234 --> 00:52:38,234
 I'm going to make sure you don't get caught.

648
00:52:38,234 --> 00:52:41,934
 - Hee Seop. 
 - Just hurry up!

649
00:52:46,484 --> 00:52:51,594
 Do you think I can live if I lost you, too?

650
00:53:01,204 --> 00:53:03,154
 Hee Seop.

651
00:53:11,264 --> 00:53:14,084
 My poor child...

652
00:53:14,084 --> 00:53:16,184
 My pitiful child...

653
00:53:16,184 --> 00:53:18,674
 What do I do...

654
00:53:20,104 --> 00:53:21,704
 Yoo Seop...

655
00:53:21,704 --> 00:53:24,054
 Hee Seop...

656
00:53:24,054 --> 00:53:28,704
 have pity on each other...

657
00:53:28,704 --> 00:53:33,084
 and two of you should take good care of each other

658
00:53:33,084 --> 00:53:36,124
 and live a good life. Okay?

659
00:53:36,124 --> 00:53:40,234
 You must survive, okay?

660
00:53:45,984 --> 00:53:48,234
Mom...

661
00:53:50,444 --> 00:53:53,114
I'm so scared...

662
00:54:18,294 --> 00:54:21,164
I am the one they are looking for.

663
00:54:22,224 --> 00:54:24,164
Please.

664
00:54:25,804 --> 00:54:27,804
Please.

665
00:54:27,804 --> 00:54:31,554
Please take me to my brother.

666
00:55:00,874 --> 00:55:02,804
Let's go inside.

667
00:55:04,544 --> 00:55:06,514
Yoon Young.

668
00:55:20,160 --> 00:55:26,750

669
00:55:26,750 --> 00:55:30,710

670
00:55:32,190 --> 00:55:34,224
You're saying he's here?

671
00:55:34,224 --> 00:55:36,114
Inside here?

672
00:55:36,114 --> 00:55:37,564
Yes.

673
00:55:37,564 --> 00:55:39,994
I saw him with my own eyes.

674
00:55:40,724 --> 00:55:42,344
I'll bring him.

675
00:55:42,344 --> 00:55:43,964
No.

676
00:55:43,964 --> 00:55:45,634
That's not a good way.

677
00:55:45,634 --> 00:55:48,364
I have an idea. Don't worry.

678
00:55:48,364 --> 00:55:49,664
Just wait here.

679
00:55:49,664 --> 00:55:52,654
There's no good way in this situation.

680
00:55:52,654 --> 00:55:55,714
If anything happens to Hee Seop in my place,

681
00:55:55,714 --> 00:55:59,704
I can no longer... I can no longer live.

682
00:55:59,704 --> 00:56:04,124
If my way works and Hee Seop is released,

683
00:56:04,124 --> 00:56:08,074
then could you please take good care of him?

684
00:56:13,104 --> 00:56:15,624
It's dangerous, so wait here.

