00:56:26,754 --> 00:56:30,550

686
00:56:43,820 --> 00:56:48,710

687
00:56:49,790 --> 00:56:55,680

688
00:56:58,170 --> 00:57:05,180

689
00:57:06,744 --> 00:57:14,600
♫  The footsteps that slowed down before we knew it  ♫

690
00:57:15,424 --> 00:57:21,290
♫  The tired look as you stand on the road  ♫

691
00:57:22,324 --> 00:57:25,420
♫  In the end  ♫

692
00:57:26,534 --> 00:57:37,420
♫  What were you looking for again that you didn't even know it was here  ♫

693
00:57:39,174 --> 00:57:45,060
♫  Are you still wandering?  ♫

