00:57:58,474 --> 00:58:05,380
♫  Standing alone here where there's no light  ♫

696
00:58:06,254 --> 00:58:14,114
♫  When you cry over even a small difficulty  ♫

697
00:58:14,114 --> 00:58:17,694
♫  Above my tired shoulders  ♫

698
00:58:17,694 --> 00:58:21,344
Are you all right?

