00:58:36,734 --> 00:58:39,564
I did something wrong

702
00:58:39,564 --> 00:58:43,924
so isn't it reasonable to receive punishment?

703
00:58:43,924 --> 00:58:46,784
What did you do wrong?

704
00:58:46,784 --> 00:58:49,740
I must've done something wrong.

705
00:58:52,200 --> 00:58:54,700
That must be why...

706
00:58:56,544 --> 00:59:00,044
everything turned out like this.

