00:59:30,354 --> 00:59:33,554
Do you know what we did wrong?

714
00:59:33,554 --> 00:59:35,584
Do you know?

715
00:59:35,584 --> 00:59:38,884
 Who am I?

716
00:59:38,884 --> 00:59:43,730
 And where is this place?

717
00:59:44,974 --> 00:59:54,194
♫  Without any words, pulling me into your arms  ♫

