01:00:24,700 --> 01:00:29,680
♫  ...pulling me into your arms  ♫

726
01:00:29,680 --> 01:00:34,350

727
01:00:34,350 --> 01:00:41,324
♫  The way you mean something to me  ♫

728
01:00:41,324 --> 01:00:47,684
